Package: quantogram
Type: Package
Title: geoms extending ggplot2 for special density and histogram plots
Version: 0.1.1
Author: Xavier Timbeau
Maintainer: X. Timbeau <xavier.timbeau@sciencespo.fr>
Description: Extend density and histogram to calculate mass (non normalized y's)
    and to bin x according to quantiles.
    Plus possibly transforming x scale on quantiles to garantee surface = mass.
